        <p class="text-justify" style="text-indent: 10%">eScience is a cloud-based integrated service platform for big data analytics offered by GRNET and the associated 
            <a href="http://okeanos.grnet.gr" target="_blank">~okeanos</a> <span data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="auto-right" data-trigger='hover focus click' data-title="Infrastructure as a Service">IaaS</span>.
