        <p class="text-justify">Furthermore, a number of other {{#link-to 'help.images'}}pre-cooked images{{/link-to}} with Hadoop-centered software is available for faster, easier and friendlier development: Ecosystem (Pig, Hive, HBase, Oozie, Flume, Spark), Cloudera, Hue.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col col-sm-6">
        <p class="text-justify">Researchers, university students and teachers can fully exploit the MapReduce (as well as others) programming paradigm without wasting time and resources in hardware, software setup, etc.</p>
        <p class="text-justify">In order to aid them in everyday research work, {{#link-to 'help.vreimages'}}VM images{{/link-to}} with a range of installed software (wiki, project management, portal setup, teleconference and digital repositories) can also be deployed through the orka VRE (Virtual Research Environment) options.</p>
